### 알림 발송 요청 등록
POST http://localhost:8080/api/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipientId": 1,
  "notificationType": "ENROLLMENT_COMPLETE",
  "channel": "EMAIL",
  "eventId": "event-123",
  "referenceId": "lecture-456"
}

### 중복 요청 (동일 eventId - 기존 건 반환)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipientId": 1,
  "notificationType": "ENROLLMENT_COMPLETE",
  "channel": "EMAIL",
  "eventId": "event-123",
  "referenceId": "lecture-456"
}

### eventId 누락 - 400 에러
POST http://localhost:8080/api/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipientId": 1,
  "notificationType": "ENROLLMENT_COMPLETE",
  "channel": "EMAIL"
}
